cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper discusses the real-world deployment of face recognition systems for various applications, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The applications mentioned in the paper involve human-computer interaction and monitoring, which can also be categorized under human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of wearable devices and webcam images also suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
